	================== Reference to Tags ================== Tasks -> List of 
	tasks which could be performed by using the clafer Task -> An individual 
	task with its configurable properties Questions -> List of questions under 
	a given task Question -> An individual question with nested answers def -> 
	question text which will be displayed to user display -> answers to be displayed 
	to user refClafer -> clafer reference to the question Answers -> List of 
	answers and their mapping for a particular question Answer -> An individual 
	answer with nested mapping of value and the operator value -> text displayed 
	to user , substring of Question.def ref -> Value to be passed to clafer for 
	a given answer operator-> Numerical value between 1-6 , which will be further 
	mapped to mathematical operator >,<,<=,>=,= respectively (value 6 is used 
	for groupcard) dependencies-> List of dependencies for a particular answer. 
	dependency -> An individual dependency refClafer -> clafer reference to the 
	dependency value -> Value to be passed to clafer for a given answer operator 
	-> Numerical value between 1-6 , which will be further mapped to mathematical 
	operator >,<,<=,>=,= respectively (value 6 is used for groupcard) -->
<Tasks>
	<Task name="c0_SymmetricEncryption">
		<Questions>
			<Question
				def="What is the level of security that you need for your data?"
				display="Very secure:Secure:Not important (I'm just testing for now and would prefer something fast)">
				<Answers>
					<Answer value="Very secure">
							<dependancy refClafer="keySize" value="128" operator="1" />
					</Answer>
					<Answer value="Secure">
							<dependancy refClafer="keySize" value="128" operator="4" />
					</Answer>
					<Answer
						value="Not important (I'm just testing for now and would prefer something fast)" />
					<!-- <dependancies> <dependancy refClafer="keySize" value="128" operator="2" 
						/> </dependancies> -->
				</Answers>
			</Question>
		</Questions>
	</Task>
</Tasks>